import React from 'react'
import { Route, Routes} from 'react-router-dom'
import App from '../App'
import test from './test'

    const Main = () => {
        return (
            <Routes>
                <Route exact path='/' component={App}>
                    <Route exact path='test/' component={test}/>
                </Route>
            </Routes>
        )
    }

export default Main
